                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable C</hi> 129.) I was in the Circus, that evening—the prosecutor had the prisoner, and gave him into my cus<lb></lb>tody with this handkerchief—I asked the prisoner how he came to do it while the gentleman was relieving him—he said I might go to the devil; I had got the handkerchief, and what did I want to <hi rend="italic">chaff</hi> him for.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183505110042"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I asked him for 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. and he gave it to me; after he was gone I found the handkerchief—he came back and asked me if I had found a handkerchief—I said I had, and gave it to him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. KING</hi>. He denied at first that he had it.</p>
